y J, Megaw T, Brown H.  <span class="ref-journal">National Patient Record Analytical Service &#x02013; ERDIP phase 2 &#x02013; Report from Bradford Project.</span> Bradford: Bradford Health Informatics Service; 2003. pp. 20\xe2\x80\x9325.<a href="http://www.nhsia.nhs.uk/erdip/pages/demonstrator/brad/bradford_(15).pdf" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" ref="reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=343292&amp;issue-id=10204&amp;journal-id=122&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI" target="_blank">http://www.nhsia.nhs.uk/erdip/pages/demonstrator/brad/bradford_(15).pdf</a> <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=National+Patient+Record+Analytical+Service+&#x02013;+ERDIP+phase+2+&#x02013;+Report+from+Bradford+Project&amp;author=J+Parry&amp;author=T+Megaw&amp;author=H+Brown&amp;publication_year=2003&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=343292&amp;issue-id=10204&amp;journal-id=122&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=Content%20Provider%7CLink%7CGoogle%20Scholar">Google Scholar</a>]</span></span></li><li id="B46"><span class="citation">Stockport Health Authority and other partners  . <span class="ref-journal">The Information Strategy for Stockport Local Health Community &#x02013; Full Local Implementation Strategy.</span> Stockport; 2000. p. 26.<a href="http://www.doh.gov.uk/ipu/implemen/flis/stockportflis.doc" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" ref="reftype=extlink&amp;article-id=343292&amp;issue-id=10204&amp;journal-id=122&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;TO=External%7CLink%7CURI" target="_blank">http://www.doh.gov.uk/ipu/implemen/flis/stockportflis.doc</a> <span class="nowrap">[<a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=The+Information+Strategy+for+Stockport+Local+Health+Community+&#x02013;+Full+Local+Implementation+Strategy&amp;publication_year=2000&amp;" target="pmc_ext" ref="reftype=other&amp;article-id=343292&amp;issue-id=10204&amp;journal-id=122&amp;FROM=Article%7CCitationRef&amp;